snippet.title: Discovery Freelancer - Official 5.1: Aftershock Release Trailer
snippet.description:
AFTERSHOCK is the next major update to the Discovery mod, featuring a vast amount of new and improved content. Explore perilous alien lairs, uncover ancient secrets and navigate devastating conflicts. 

*Story Mode - Freelancer: HD Edition* 
• Download: https://www.moddb.com/mods/freelancer-hd-edition
• Discord: https://discord.com/invite/ScqgYuFqmU
• Features: Adds new textures, compatibility improvements, bug fixes and much more! 

*Multiplayer - Discovery* 
• Download: https://discoverygc.com/forums/showthread.php?tid=126999
• Discord: https://discord.com/invite/FdSkbZ8 
• Features: Adds new systems, ships, role play and much more! 

*Video Credits*
• Jammi - Editor
